01:28:41.000 --> 01:28:47.000
shareholders set tasks in the category of these two aspects.

01:28:47.000 --> 01:28:52.000
These formulas can be used universally for any type of business,

01:28:52.000 --> 01:29:01.000
and they are the main ones on the basis of which you can determine the quality of management in the company

01:29:01.000 --> 01:29:08.000
and, accordingly, determine the motivational component of the entire management team of the enterprise.

